title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Retreating from a busy schedule to attune with your own inner wisdom is restorative. Fortunately, the still, small voice of your higher self is always standing by, ready to speak with you. But you can habitually tune this sage advice out to listen to other less useful input. Losing connection with the source of your own insight puts you at the mercy of relying on others. Thankfully, it doesnt require much to reconnect because nature will rush to fill a vacuum. Ironically, quiet time with no expectations and no external noises brings the answers you seek. You only need to create enough space for the magic to happen. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
